OL,3,CWales is better off now than before
OL,4,Cthe 1984 miners' strike, says Lord
OL,5,CHeseltine
OL,7,FAsked if Wales is better off now, he
OL,8,Fsaid: "There's no question it's better
OL,9,Foff. If you look at all the statistics
OL,10,Fabout people's living standards, they
OL,11,Fhave been transformed over the periods
OL,12,Fwe are talking about."
OL,14,FHe was also asked if would he
OL,15,Fapologise, as many Labour and Plaid
OL,16,FCymru politicians have called for.
OL,18,FLord Heseltine's response was "No, I
OL,19,Fwouldn't apologise for anything that I
OL,20,Fdid."
