OL,5,CHeseltine
OL,7,F"But in order to get there I used to
OL,8,Fdrive down the road through the
OL,9,FValleys and one saw the contrast. So
OL,10,Fone knew about the sort of feeling and
OL,11,Fthe anxieties and they were all wholly
OL,12,Flegitimate.
OL,14,F"But there was another thought. Do I
OL,15,Freally believe it's a good idea for
OL,16,Fyoung boys from their earliest age to
OL,17,Fgo down the pit to a dangerous,
OL,18,Funhealthy way of life?"
